
 If you want to contribute to this project, check this TODO list :)

 - more servers:
     write a lot of xml files in order to support 
     more translation web services

 - --list-servers
   --list-langpairs

 - utf-8 output support

 - Autodetection of new server files

 - Show all the avaliables translations in each server

 - Servers autoupdate
     reddo update

 - Translate a text when receiving only the langpair, for example 
